OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FThe chief constable of Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice has told a public inquiry Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane should have been arrested
OL,10,Fprior to the attacks - when a warrant
OL,11,Fwas issued after he failed to appear
OL,12,Fin court months before he killed three
OL,13,Fpeople and injured three others.
OL,15,FShe apologised at today's hearing, and
OL,16,Fsaid there were "no excuses" for why
OL,17,FCalocane was not arrested after a
OL,18,Fwarrant was issued when he was charged
OL,19,Fwith assaulting an emergency worker
OL,20,Fbut failed to appear in court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
