OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FThe inquiry heard details of the
OL,8,Fwarrant were sent by Leicestershire
OL,9,FPolice to Nottinghamshire Police on
OL,10,FSeptember 23, 2022 by means of an
OL,11,F"occurrence" on the police's
OL,12,Finformation management system.
OL,14,FThat went into an inbox on the system
OL,15,Fthe same day, but the inbox was not
OL,16,Fregularly checked and there were no
OL,17,Frecorded updates on executing the
OL,18,Fwarrant before the day of the
OL,19,FNottingham attacks in June the next
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,F"That is unacceptable," Ms Meynell
OL,8,Fsaid. "Our processes around warrants
OL,9,Fweren't adequate. We weren't able to
OL,10,Fprioritise execution of warrants.
OL,12,F"It is something I fully accept
OL,13,Fresponsibility for and have apologised
OL,14,Fin my statement, but I want to
OL,15,Freiterate that apology, it is
OL,16,Funacceptable and our processes weren't
OL,17,Fas they should have been."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@WO]pD@GOUtD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FWhen asked by counsel to the inquiry
OL,8,FRachel Langdale KC why she thought
OL,9,Fthat was the case, Ms Meynell said she
OL,10,Fbelieves officers were not using the
OL,11,Fsystem properly.
OL,13,FMs Meynell said Nottinghamshire Police
OL,14,Fhas "completely changed" the way
OL,15,Fwarrants are managed following the
OL,16,Ffatal attacks and have new processes
OL,17,Fin place which see warrants reviewed
OL,18,Fon a daily basis.
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FShe admitted Calocane should have been
OL,8,Farrested and agreed when Ms Langdale
OL,9,Fsaid there were "no excuses"
OL,10,Finstitutionally as to why he was not.
OL,12,FMs Meynell said: "Nottinghamshire
OL,13,FPolice should have made inquiries to
OL,14,Ftry and locate him in order to execute
OL,15,Fthat warrant.
OL,17,F"I accept on behalf of Nottinghamshire
OL,18,FPolice that VC should have been
OL,19,Farrested in relation to that fail to
OL,20,Fappear warrant."
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@\O]tD@ROUyD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FShe added: "I fully accept we should
OL,8,Fhave arrested him. My experience of
OL,9,Fthe type of assault he was wanted for,
OL,10,Fhe would have been bailed from
OL,11,Fmagistrates (had he been arrested) and
OL,12,Fpotentially it wouldn't have been
OL,13,Fprogressed with due to his mental
OL,14,Fhealth status at the time."
OL,16,FDiscussing a policy relating to the
OL,17,Fway police deal with people with
OL,18,Fmental ill health, Ms Meynell admitted
OL,19,Fit had not been "understood on the
OL,20,Fground" by officers.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@[O]{D@QOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FThe policy said a suspect having
OL,8,Fmental ill-health or learning
OL,9,Fdifficulties should not preclude a
OL,10,Ffull investigation and there was a
OL,11,F"misconception" that arrest, interview
OL,12,Fand prosecution of persons with mental
OL,13,Fdisorder should not be considered due
OL,14,Fto mental capacity issues or the
OL,15,Fpublic interest.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FAsked if she thought Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice had a "sufficiently
OL,9,Finvestigative culture around
OL,10,Fpolicing", Ms Meynell said: "I think
OL,11,Fthat now there is, I think at this
OL,12,Ftime there wasn't.
OL,14,F"We have put a lot in place to improve
OL,15,Four investigations and they certainly
OL,16,Fare improved, but at the time there
OL,17,Fwere some shortcomings, that is why we
OL,18,Fhave made the changes."
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@IO]rD@]OUvD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774253648
OL,3,CNottingham attacks inquiry: Calocane
OL,4,Cshould have been arrested months
OL,5,Cearlier
OL,7,FAsked what the shortcomings were, Ms
OL,8,FMeynell added: "It is difficult for me
OL,9,Fto go into those details because I
OL,10,Fcan't recall exactly what they were
OL,11,Fand I don't want to not do them
OL,12,Fjustice.
OL,14,F"Our investigative plan addressed
OL,15,Fthose shortcomings."
OL,17,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@pD@POUvD@AOUwD@TO]
